

Install driver for leap motion sensor:

install driver (32 or 64 bit version) from SVN
(in LeapMotionDriver):

  sudo dpkg -i Leap-2.0.1+15831-64x.deb

copy the following files from the SVN
(in LeapMotionDriver/additional_files/include, 
LeapMotionDriver/additional_files/lib/x64 or
LeapMotionDriver/additional_files/lib/x86):

  sudo cp Leap.h Leap.i LeapMath.h /usr/local/include
  sudo cp libLeap.so /usr/lib/Leap


